terminal-pong
------------------------------------------
Classic ping-pong game written in c++17 and played in terminal

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libncursesw10-6.5+20240427-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/kumaran-14/terminal-pong

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/kumaran-14/terminal-pong/archive/refs/tags/1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack terminal-pong-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./terminal-pong-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/terminal-pong-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/terminal-pong-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(terminal-pong)
  /usr/bin/pong.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/terminal-pong.README
  /usr/share/doc/terminal-pong/README.md

------------------

